*mariadb-10.0.12 (29 Jul 2014)

  29 Jul 2014; Robin H. Johnson <robbat2@gentoo.org> +mariadb-10.0.12.ebuild:
  Bring MySQL 5.6/MariaDB 10.0 from the overlay into the tree. Thanks to the
  great work of Brian Evans <grknight@gentoo.org>. ~arm temporarily dropped
  pending bug #518506.

